Came during lunch with a friend. I enjoyed the food and the staff. The food had good flavor. Not the best Gyro I have had but better then average. My friend really liked the fry sauce. I would eat here again. I want to bring my husband.
Ate:
Gyro Sandwich (lamb) w/ salad
Baklava

Food was on point! Tasted fresh and delicious! I‚Äôve had Gyros while I was in Greece and those were amazing, these are not far from that. The sauce is so refreshing and tasty, meat was cooked thoroughly and perfectly. Tasty bread and fresh veg! Potatoes were hot and seasoned as well as the fries. The white walls and painting remind me of being in Greece. The seating is simple and casual. I only think they need a slight renovation to paint and old seating/ tables but it‚Äôs nothing to worry about. All in all a great little gem and delicious food.

****************This is a good little gem, food was good. Service was good. Was not sure what to get so I got the combo plate to make sure I try a little of everything.

üëéüëéThe only thing I didn't like was having to pay a forced 4% transaction fee for using a credit or debit card. I think it should be all encompassed into the price point vs having to pay more if you don't have cash. Almost just like a forced tip so to speak before you even try your food. Not that big of deal just my opinion I wanted to share. üòâ But Maravel was great and friendly. They do have a free drink on Mondays if that is your thing. üëç (that was also a surprise in not in a bad way) üòÇ üëç

Only other miss was that it was 83 degrees inside on a 62 degree day. They had a guy here working on swamp coolers but was unable to resolve at the time he was telling staff. I opened their side door and created a little cross wind.

Best Greek food around. I beg my family to go with me at least every other week!

The food is fresh and light, it's a pretty healthy option that still tastes amazing.
If you enjoy fresh, delicious, and a tasty variety of Greek food, this is the place. It is a clean and friendly atmosphere. I will 10/10 recommend eating here. Food comes out fast and tastes amazing!
